Should not be used in place of more permanent relationships between demographic entities. ">EXTRACT_PARTICIPATION</a><a name="EXTRACT_PARTICIPATION"> </a></td><td style="vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px" class="hierarchy"><a style="padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; border: 1px maroon solid; font-weight: bold; color: #301212; background-color: #fdf4f4;; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; border: 1px maroon solid; font-weight: bold; color: #301212; background-color: #fdf4f4;" href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/conformance-rules.html#constraints" title="This element has or is affected by constraints ( Function_valid, Mode_valid )">C</a></td><td style="vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px" class="hierarchy">0..*</td><td style="vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px" class="hierarchy"><a href="StructureDefinition-Any.html">Any</a></td><td style="vertical-align: top; text-align : var(--ig-left,left); background-color: white; border: 0px #F0F0F0 solid; padding:0px 4px 0px 4px" class="hierarchy">Model of a participation of a Party (any Actor or Role) in an activity.<br class="constraint"/><span title="null" class="constraint">Constraints: </span><span style="font-weight:bold" title="Function valid must be present" class="constraint">Function_valid</span><span title="null" class="constraint">, </span><span style="font-weight:bold" title="Mode valid must be present" class="constraint">Mode_valid</span><br/></td></tr>
