      <path value="EXTRACT_PARTICIPATION"/>
      <short value="Model of a participation of a Party (any Actor or Role) in an activity."/>
      <definition value="Model of a participation of a Party (any Actor or Role) in an activity.  Used to represent any participation of a Party in some activity, which is not  explicitly in the model, e.g. assisting nurse. Can be used to record past or  future participations.&#xA;&#xA;Should not be used in place of more permanent relationships between demographic entities. "/>
      <min value="0"/>
      <max value="*"/>
      <base>
